INFO_HOW_TO_WORK: ¬øHow can several managers work at the same time?
INFO_HOW_TO_WORK_ANSWER: The first creates its assignments, exports the data from the home section and leaves it in a site shared by those responsible, the second imports it and creates its assignments, and so on.
INFO__CONTACT: ¬øHow do I report a bug or an improvement?
INFO__DISTRIBUTION_ANSWER: Yes, although it is recommended that you distribute the download link, as a new version may have come out with some correction.
INFO__HOW_TO_SEND_ASSIGNMENTS_ANSWER: When generating an assignment in the -Assignments- section, an assignment sheet appears in the -Image- column. We click on it and we can preview the assignment. Then below, we can copy it to the clipboard to later paste it in whatsapp web, generate a .png image or generate a pdf.
INFO__WHAT_CAN_BE_DONE_ANSWER: All kinds of assignments can be created. You need to create the assignment types, rooms, and participants in advance.
INFO__WHAT_IS_SERVIHELPER_ANSWER: It is a program that runs on the machine. Your data is managed internally, so it never goes to the internet.
